data.description: Welcome to this beautifully upgraded 3-bedroom, 2-bath home nestled in the heart of Williamston, SC. Situated on a generous corner lot, this residence boasts a perfect blend of modern comforts and classic charm. Step inside to discover a thoughtfully renovated interior, including new flooring throughout, completely renovated second bathroom, new kitchen layout with new cabinets, and new paint and trim throughout. The spacious living areas are adorned with new fixtures, and the updated kitchen showcases sleek appliances and ample storage. Retreat to the master suite with its private bath and large closet space. Enjoy the convenience of two additional bedrooms, perfect for a growing family or a home office. The exterior reveals many updates including a new roof in 2021, and new gutters as well as a charming front porch. With its numerous improvements and prime location, this home is a true gem in Williamston, promising a lifestyle of comfort.
